  "A nation has a high HDI (0.92) but a very high ecological footprint (9 gha per person). Another nation has a moderate HDI (0.72) and a low ecological footprint (1.5 gha per person). What does this comparison reveal about the relationship between human development and environmental sustainability?": "",
